{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8b424174cc","title":"中央关于印行农业生产互助合作正式决议的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0c71b626d3","index":0,"year":1953,"month":2,"day":15,"articleId":"8b424174cc"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8f7942ce15","type":"title","text":"中央关于印行农业生产互助合作正式决议的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8b424174cc"},{"id":"9de58e9cf6","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8b424174cc"},{"id":"f0b1d63292","type":"appellation","text":"中央各部委、中央人民政府各党组；各中央局、分局，并转各省市委：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8b424174cc"},{"id":"859f765bee","type":"paragraph","text":"中央于一九五一年十二月所发关于农业生产互助合作的决议草案，经一年多的实施证明是正确的，应即作为正式决议，将“草案”二字删去。只将该草案第十一条内“并有机器条件”六字改为“和有适当经济条件”八字。此决议可即照此印行单行本。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8b424174cc"},{"id":"121bce6e68","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央二月十五日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8b424174cc"}],"page":{"id":"c901f0123f","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"8b424174cc","start":0,"end":0}},"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"f7cfd13057","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8b424174cc","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共中央1951年12月15日关于农业生产互助合作的决议草案第十一条中这一段话的原文是：“国营农场应当推广，以发挥它的示范作用，并给互助组和合作社以技术上的援助和指导。在农民完全同意并有机器条件的地方，亦可试办少数社会主义性质的集体农庄，例如每省有一个至几个，以便取得经验，并为农民示范。1953年3月，毛泽东和中央又对这个决议作了修改，并于1953年3月26日在《人民日报》上发表。"}],"contents":[{"id":"3fcfd40555","type":"subtitle","text":"市委：","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8b424174cc"},{"id":"49d6e06a9a","type":"subtitle","text":"中央","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8b424174cc"},{"id":"8e253c0244","type":"paragraph","text":"二月十五日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8b424174cc"},{"id":"ea254e9d48","type":"paragraph","text":"中央于一九五一年十二月所发关于农业生产互助合作的决议草案，经一年多的实施证明是正确的，应即作为正式决议，将“草案”二字删去。只将该草案第十一条内“并有机器条件”六字改为“和有适当经济条件”八字。叫此决议可即照此印行单行本。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8b424174cc"},{"id":"f4b76b7ca8","type":"title","text":"中央关于印行农业生产互助合作正式决议的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8b424174cc"},{"id":"f7cfd13057","type":"paragraph","text":"中央各部委、中央人民政府各党组；各中央局、分局，并转各省","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8b424174cc"}],"page":{"id":"725d4df887","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8b424174cc","start":496,"end":496}}}},"__N_SSG":true}